data.description: This amazing home in the sought after community of Boca Bay Colony is just waiting for you! Newly remodeled in 2020 from top to bottom. Newly installed  chandeliers, additional inset canned lights, automated Hunter Douglas blinds & custom drapery. This house has exceptional living space and storage!  The remodeled kitchen features SubZero Refrigerator/Freezer, Wolf stovetop & double ovens, Miele coffee maker, Perlick beverage cooler and under-counter 2 drawer refrigerator.  Lighted display cabinets w/etched glass, quartz countertops, pullout storage cabinets and spice drawers complete this chef's dream. HUGE Owners suite with direct access to the resort style pool w/sun shelf & hot tub. Fenced in backyard has complete privacy. SEE DOCUMENTS FOR ALL UPGRADES
